{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c4dd9a0e89","title":"同王明等谈中共在抗日战争中的路线方针","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4bd9f9d0fe","index":0,"year":1937,"month":11,"day":11,"articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"}],"tags":[{"id":"1f0832775e","name":"王明","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","name":"斯大林选集（诸夏怀斯社2017年5月）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"斯大林，诸夏怀斯社2017年5月","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1332d101b8","name":"斯大林"}]},"publication_details":{"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1828281df0","type":"paragraph","text":"同王明等谈中共在抗日战争中的路线方针","index":0,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"ea7c185090","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年11月11日）","index":1,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"d040827b5d","type":"paragraph","text":"在克里姆林宫同斯大林谈话。","index":2,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"642406495f","type":"paragraph","text":"季米特洛夫、王明、康生、王橡祥。","index":3,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"a9dd96f2dd","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林：共产国际书记处的决定已经过时了。","index":4,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"b968cb8919","type":"paragraph","text":"“这就是人们坐在办公室里宾思苦想的结果！”","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"84a306c52c","type":"paragraph","text":"“要用一切手段加强对托派的斗争”（决定中的话）。“这是不够的。托派必须追捕、枪、消灭。他们是全世界的好细、最恶毒的法西斯走狗！”","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"d84ecb9913","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）对于中国共产党现在基本的问题是：融入全民族的浪潮并取得领导地位。","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"772cd8d215","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）现在主要的问题是战争，而不是土地革命、没收土地。","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"c9cfad7e16","type":"paragraph","text":"（税收必须有利于战争。）","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"e5e41b3785","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党人从一个极端走到另一个极端一一以前是没收一切；现在是什么都不没收。","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"c097ef2ed9","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）口号就是一个：","index":11,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"640b63b671","type":"paragraph","text":"“争取中国人民独立的胜利战争。","index":12,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"6d61915203","type":"paragraph","text":"“争取自由中国，反对日本侵略者。”","index":13,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"646e133168","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）中国人怎样打击外部敌人—一这是决定性的问题。当这一间题结束时再提出怎样互相打的问题！","index":14,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"1b590b602e","type":"paragraph","text":"1）土明时社中共驻共产国际代表，此次谈话后即回延安，却完全违背斯大林的谈话精神，竭力推行所谓“一切通过统一战线，一切服从统一战线”的右倾投降主义路线。一一本书编者注","index":15,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"36e60d3140","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）现在中国人所处的条件比我们在1918-1920年时的条件更加有利。","index":16,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"9a6f14541a","type":"paragraph","text":"当时在我们这里，国家在社会革命方面是被分割的","index":17,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"9466a0fb69","type":"paragraph","text":"在中国，民族革命、争取民族独立和自由，把国家和人民团结起来了。","index":18,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"15c1942659","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）中国有巨大的人力资源，我认为蒋介石说中国将取得胜利是对的。只是必须在已经打响的战争中坚持下来。","index":19,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"42b9f38c84","type":"paragraph","text":"（7）因此必须创建自己的军事工业。","index":20,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"1c80311649","type":"paragraph","text":"生产飞机。飞机容易生产，但是运输很困难。","index":21,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"7ac8b844a0","type":"paragraph","text":"（我们会提供制造飞机的材料！）必须创立飞机制造业","index":22,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"f074080322","type":"paragraph","text":"还要生产坦克。","index":23,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"5ba73cf4f5","type":"paragraph","text":"（制造坦克的材料我们能够提供！）","index":24,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"c7bca58223","type":"paragraph","text":"如果中国有自己的军事工业，谁都不可能战胜它。","index":25,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"a029051b4b","type":"paragraph","text":"（8）八路军必须要有30个师，而不是3个师","index":26,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"57ff31e3b0","type":"paragraph","text":"这可以通过建立后备团的形式做到，以便补充现有的师","index":27,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"fa5dd5f3d7","type":"paragraph","text":"必须建立新的团队。要日夜进行军事训练。","index":28,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"1d91b8c7cd","type":"paragraph","text":"（9）在八路军还没有炮兵的时候，它的策略不该是直接进攻，而应该是缝扰敌人，把他们引进自已一方并在后方打击他们","index":29,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"e4045eb181","type":"paragraph","text":"必须炸毁日本军队的交通线、铁路桥。","index":30,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"f193c899eb","type":"paragraph","text":"（10）不管英国还是美国，它们都不愿意中国胜利。出于它们帝国主义的利益，它们害怕中国胜利","index":31,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"99574fc20c","type":"paragraph","text":"中国的胜利将影响印度、印度支那等。","index":32,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"a1efe2afbe","type":"paragraph","text":"它们希望日本由于打仗而削弱，但是不允许中国站起来。","index":33,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"505bfda72f","type":"paragraph","text":"它们希望有日本这条挂起来的狗吓晓中国，就像过去吓晓沙皇俄国那样，但是不希望这条狗有独吞猎物的可能。","index":34,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"e90c8789c2","type":"paragraph","text":"（11）对于中国的党代表大会“来说，讨论理论问题是不适宜的理论问题可以往后放放，等到战争结束以后。","index":35,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"1b6c6f4576","type":"paragraph","text":"谈论中国发展的非资本主义道路，现在比起过去，机会更少了。","index":36,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"83c3976252","type":"paragraph","text":"（资本主义在中国不是止在发展吗！）","index":37,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"c3088b88de","type":"paragraph","text":"（12）建立民族革命联盟的问题记退未决","index":38,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"db43435da3","type":"paragraph","text":"（13）在武汉的八路军和党的合适的代表","index":39,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"b9531d9201","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集》《季米特洛夫日记选编2002年版第59—61页","index":40,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"622db14364","type":"paragraph","text":"档案附卷七第269—271页","index":41,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"},{"id":"b89c34a0eb","type":"paragraph","text":"①指当时中国共产党准备召开的第七次代表大会。一—本书编者注","index":42,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89"}],"page":{"id":"06f253a2d7","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"c4dd9a0e89","start":2709,"end":2711}}}},"__N_SSG":true}